    "en": {
      "title": "UNP puts religion first and starts the anniversary celebration",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "On the occasion of the United National Party's 76th anniversary celebration, all religions will be held at five places tomorrow (4), UNP Deputy Leader and Senior Advisor to the President Ruwan Wijayawardena said.",
        "These religious ceremonies will be held at Kollupitiya Waluka Ramaya, Kochchikade Shivam Temple, Kochchikade Saint Anthony Church, Colombo Dawata Gaha Church and Hunupitiya Gangarama Temple.",
        "Deputy Leader Ruwan Wijayawardena, President Vajira Abeywardena, National Organizer Sagala Ratnayake, General Secretary Palitha Range Bandara, Vice Leader Akila Viraj Kariyawasam, Lakwanitha Chairperson Shantini Kongahage will participate in these events.",
        "The 76th anniversary of the United National Party is on September 6."
      ],
